{"thag10.4:0.1":"Theragatha 10.4 ","thag10.4:0.2":"Dasakanipata ","thag10.4:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag10.4:0.4":"Culapanthakattheragatha ","thag10.4:1.1":"“Dandha mayham gati asi, ","thag10.4:1.2":"paribhuto pure aham; ","thag10.4:1.3":"Bhata ca mam panamesi, ","thag10.4:1.4":"‘gaccha dani tuvam gharam’. ","thag10.4:2.1":"Soham panamito santo, ","thag10.4:2.2":"sangharamassa kotthake; ","thag10.4:2.3":"Dummano tattha atthasim, ","thag10.4:2.4":"sasanasmim apekkhava. ","thag10.4:3.1":"Bhagava tattha agacchi, ","thag10.4:3.2":"sisam mayham paramasi; ","thag10.4:3.3":"Bahaya mam gahetvana, ","thag10.4:3.4":"sangharamam pavesayi. ","thag10.4:4.1":"Anukampaya me sattha, ","thag10.4:4.2":"padasi padapunchanim; ","thag10.4:4.3":"‘Etam suddham adhitthehi, ","thag10.4:4.4":"ekamantam svadhitthitam’. ","thag10.4:5.1":"Tassaham vacanam sutva, ","thag10.4:5.2":"vihasim sasane rato; ","thag10.4:5.3":"Samadhim patipadesim, ","thag10.4:5.4":"uttamatthassa pattiya. ","thag10.4:6.1":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","thag10.4:6.2":"dibbacakkhu visodhitam; ","thag10.4:6.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thag10.4:6.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thag10.4:7.1":"Sahassakkhattumattanam, ","thag10.4:7.2":"nimminitvana panthako; ","thag10.4:7.3":"Nisidambavane ramme, ","thag10.4:7.4":"yava kalappavedana. ","thag10.4:8.1":"Tato me sattha pahesi, ","thag10.4:8.2":"dutam kalappavedakam; ","thag10.4:8.3":"Paveditamhi kalamhi, ","thag10.4:8.4":"vehasadupasankamim. ","thag10.4:9.1":"Vanditva satthuno pade, ","thag10.4:9.2":"ekamantam nisidaham; ","thag10.4:9.3":"Nisinnam mam viditvana, ","thag10.4:9.4":"atha sattha patiggahi. ","thag10.4:10.1":"Ayago sabbalokassa, ","thag10.4:10.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","thag10.4:10.3":"Punnakkhettam manussanam, ","thag10.4:10.4":"patigganhittha dakkhinan”ti. ","thag10.4:10.5":"… Culapanthako thero …. "}